		"description": "<p dir=\"ltr\">You have become a powerful wielder of divine power and elemental might. You gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Your Wisdom score increases by +1, to a maximum of 20.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Your @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.uit7l3mc64l5h8h1]{Elemental Blast} does additional radiant or necrotic damage equal to your proficiency bonus (choose when you take this feat) to creatures of the aberration, celestial, elemental, fey, fiend, and undead types.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">When you cast a spell with a casting time of one action matching the school of an elemental affinity you have with a spell slot, or when you use @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.s4iiatrup3e3virw]{Channel Divinity} as an action, you can make a single elemental blast attack as a bonus action.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>",
